Sys_MapExt.Doc: SELECT (SELECT Lab FROM Sys_Enum WHERE EnumKey =~FaWenLeiXing~ AND IntKey = @Key) +~[~+datename(year,getdate())+~]~ + CAST((CAST(REPLACE(ISNULL(REPLACE((SELECT top 1 FaWenWenHao FROM ND150Rpt WHERE FaWenLeiXing = @Key AND WFState <> 0 AND WFState <> 1 AND FaWenWenHao IS NOT NULL AND len(FaWenWenHao) > 0 ORDER BY LEN(FaWenWenHao) DESC, FaWenWenHao DESC) , (SELECT Lab+~[~+datename(year,getdate())+~]~ FROM Sys_Enum WHERE EnumKey = ~FaWenLeiXing~ AND IntKey = @Key), ~~),~0号~),~号~,~~) AS INT) + 1) AS NVARCHAR) + ~号~ AS FaWenWenHao
